27-SEPT-JULY-2017 Matthew J. Wolf <matthew.wolf.hpsdr@speciosus.net>

Version 2.2 (Public Release)
  - Added the "all" commands.
  - Remove the need to poll the FTDI UART for state of the bits. The program
    keeps track of the state of the bits.
  - General clean up of code and comments

Version 2.1
  - Replaced polling the FIFO with select to wait for an update to the FIFO.
    Select has a lower CPU impact than polling.

Version 2.0
  - Added second bit / pin to program
  - General clean up of code and comments
   
Version 1.1
  - Added error checking 
  - Added comments

Version 1.0  
  -Initial version with basic functionality 
 
